title: BRIEF-Sodifrance H1 net result turns to profit of 0.9 mln euros
text:
BRIEF-Sodifrance H1 net result turns to profit of 0.9 mln euros Sept 23 
Sept 23 Sodifrance SA : 
* Reports H1 net income of 921,000 euros ($1.03 million) versus loss of 54,000 euros a year ago 
* H1 current operating income is 1.5 million euros versus 614,000 euros a year ago Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8961 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
